<B><I>Evoluxa</B></I></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/ukelson13.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Kelson13</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Wizard</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(10/2/01 10:22:59 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Melee dmg v caster dmg.</span><hr size=1> I agree in part, Rhuobe.  However, they do SO MUCH more damage than us which is why many Wizards take issue with this.  It's not anywhere near balanced.  We're not broken, but VI needs to get their heads out of their collective ass and adjust our damage to finally make us what we are supposed to be.  The big guns.<br>
